        <item>
            <title>2.6.2</title>
            <pubDate>Fri, 26 Jun 2026 22:24:37 +0900</pubDate>
            <link>https://github.com/Saqoosha/Canopy</link>
            <sparkle:version>68</sparkle:version>
            <sparkle:shortVersionString>2.6.2</sparkle:shortVersionString>
            <sparkle:minimumSystemVersion>15.0</sparkle:minimumSystemVersion>
            <sparkle:hardwareRequirements>arm64</sparkle:hardwareRequirements>
            <description sparkle:format="markdown"><![CDATA[### Bug Fixes
- Fixed background task hourglass icon getting stuck in the sidebar when long-running sessions streamed heavy tool output. The completion-marker scan now tracks the byte offset captured at task launch instead of a fixed 32 KB tail, so completions are always detected regardless of how much output accumulates in between.
- Moved the wake-up JSONL read off the main thread so multi-megabyte sessions no longer stall the UI when reconciling background tasks.
]]></description>
